  "texts": [
    "By inspection then, we see that we can detect any single-qubit error that occurs at the initialization step.",
    "Heavy-hex codeWe can also inject the [[4, 1, 2]] code into the heavy-hex code.",
    "This is particularly relevant with respect to the experiment presented in the main text, as the experiment is implemented on hardware that is tailored to realize the heavy-hex code.",
